data.text:
Obituary of Richard Rodgers

Rogers, Richard R. Rochester: May 27, 2011. Survived by brother, Michael; sisters, Liz (Jeff) Munson, Diana Kemp (Gene Swain); nephews, and great-nieces & nephews; caregivers, Ada Carey & Anthony Beaman; close friend, Robert West. Memorial Mass, Wednesday, 9:30 AM in St. John the Evangelist Church (West Ridge Rd.) Interment, Private. In lieu of flowers, donations to NAMI, 320 North Goodman St., #102, Rochester, NY 14607.

To send flowers to the family or plant a tree in memory of Richard Rodgers, please visit Tribute Store
